Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天 我们在这里献上诚挚的哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怀着沉重悲痛的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们将与勇者做最后的告别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮银天赋异禀 精神坚毅不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且性格善良体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}完成了神树大人交付的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她光辉的成就 将永远为我们指明道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请在神树大人的身边安宁地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}永远地 守望我们的前程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.36,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这太叫人伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.98,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么年轻的孩子 太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小银完成了自己的职责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们这些市民想象不出是什么任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过肯定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为神树大人的使命而捐躯 多大的荣誉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 但一想到如果是我的孩子死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小银做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小银成了英灵 多令人称羡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以后三之轮家的人 都能享受高额援助了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她会很骄傲的 自己能尽一份孝心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}两位勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽说是为职责而牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}失去孩子们宝贵的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}孩子的亲属朋友想必悲痛欲绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可以想到她的家属是有何等的心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮银的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}献花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神明为什么不能保护好姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}姐姐一直很努力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.98,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}铁郎 别这样 铁郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么 为什么会是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.39,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冷静点铁郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别把我的姐姐带走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神明也能做这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}偏偏在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了三三而战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果三三在 她肯定会说「干掉敌人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果是三三的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}银的话会全力突破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是银教会我的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}气势！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们成功了 三三
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}银都看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她肯定看在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}两位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你们忍痛完成了使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果刚才什么都做不到 三三会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么多可怕的经历 还尝过无比的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们依然能勇敢地面对艰巨的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们都是真正的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老师第一次这样夸奖我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最伟大的是三三啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她只身击退了三只Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以 可以别忘了三三吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她是那么强 是那么优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们不是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们三个人都是勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起 我纠正
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们三个人都是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是可怕的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有巨大的敌人会来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个梦一定是预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}战斗会更加激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也需要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早・安・啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其实我一直想问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是别人说 不能打听神树大人的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 你昨天告别式上也是去完成任务的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还好吧 会怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎？不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 可以说一下任务是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这个问题不能问本人 会被大赦消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还讲这种话 你会被消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的假的 我要被消灭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我妈妈说会把小银编入教材 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 你和鹫尾也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神树大人选中的人都好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们是神树馆的英雄 我支持你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其实我们并不想变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}同学们 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安 鹫尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然不知道发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮是为了所有人而…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她是敢于牺牲的坚强女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神树大人才选中了她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果你关心三之轮 就不要太在意我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园园
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉抱歉 我还得再快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我觉得勇者也要适时转换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫会提议出来玩 还真是太阳打西边出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}幸好老师同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天别管任务了 好好放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫也相当有气势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是父母要我穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很好看哦 像人偶一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来转个圈看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很难为情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}转得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快门时机！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂 喂 禁止拍照啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我打算拿来当待机画面的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太难为情了 别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在待机也是鹫鹫的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你看 是你吃乌冬面时的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你别这样啦 我真的很难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:28.01,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的手机我做主啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我就把园园设成我的待机画面咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的要用我的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你难道不应该害羞一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.44,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:42.30,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}买给我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好啦好啦 别哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这里要笑一笑才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}苹果糖和巧克力香蕉都太传统
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一点也不稀奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但看你很乐在其中嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然老套 但在祭典时吃起来就是好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老板 请给我两根
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我可吃不了那么多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是吗 那我吃两根
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你胃口真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好吃 这是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老板 我想把你的店都买下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打这电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.63,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好了好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}算你聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}已经没零用钱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想要那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 那个一等奖的小鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫 怎么做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冷静下来 调整呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已经清楚这把枪的特点了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}微调就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}集中精神瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要使力 慢慢收紧手指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后靠气势！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}气势！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}成功啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}竟然有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:54.94,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太棒啦 得到小鸡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这不应该会被软木塞弹打下来才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这话什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拿去吧 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了呢 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}射击可是我擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但扣下扳机的可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以这是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太棒了 耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想换成那边三个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从这里看烟火最清楚 一般人不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}准备功课做得真足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我根据旧博客文分析出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你好擅长这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有一个是三三的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也要谢谢你呢 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和我一起成为勇者的是鹫鹫和三三 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是个挺怪的女生 所以交不到什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园园才不怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要不是和你们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我可能没办法这么努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}银是冲锋陷阵的人 我则比较不会变通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要不是园园做队长 我们就是一盘散沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为是我们三个人 才能努力过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}升上六年级 各种训练和合宿好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能成为你们两位的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们三人可是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无论之后发生什么事 都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的 我接收到资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}正在确认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是 我给她们放了假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为失去一人的精神创伤还是非常大的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是 那我就先挂了
